node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '9 Rules for Starting Your Day Right S @awareness_of_success'.
Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text.
Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '9 Rules for Starting Your Day Right 3. Not drinking enough water. Having a glass of water in the morning after you wake up is crucial for you to rehydrate yourself after a whole night of not drinking. It jumpstarts your body systems to get rid of toxins, improves your digestion, and even prevents you from craving certain foods and overeating. @awareness_of_success'.
Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '9 Rules for Starting Your Day Right 5. Letting "weeds" grow in your mind. Your success success is greatly determined by the type of information you feed your mind. You must get yourself preoccupied with information that will help you progress. If you don't get yourself busy with valuable information, "weeds" can grow inside your mind. These weeds can be gossip, negativity, useless information that may distract you if your mind isn't busy enough with information beneficial for your success. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '9 Rules for Starting Your Day Right 6. Skipping on exercise. You don't have to do a 3-hour exercise a day. But give yourself at least 10 minutes to get your heart beating at a faster rate. Exercise does not only make you fitter. It's also a great way to ensure productivity. Without it, you might find that you're a little sluggish during the day. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '9 Rules for Starting Your Day Right 7. Not practicing affirmation Words are powerful. So before all the negativity creeps in and destroys your day, make sure you get into a positive mindset through affirmations, that is, saying positive things about yourself in the present tense AM." Use the power of your words. Once you get into the habit of claiming the things you want to achieve in the future as if they are already happening in your life, you'll find that you have more purpose and direction with your thoughts and actions. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '9 Rules for Starting Your Day Right 8. Drink coffee right after waking up. Most people may not accept this one since coffee has long been everyone's routine. But your body doesn't need that dose of caffeine right after you wake up. You have high cortisol levels in the morning, which is your body's built-in alarm system. So it's much better to drink your coffee in the afternoon or whenever you start to feel sleepy at work. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says '9 Rules for Starting Your Day Right Drop two below if you needed to hear this!! @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DID YOU KNOW? No one can destroy iron, but it's own rust can, likewise no one can destroy a person, but his own mindset can. @AWARENESS_OF_SUCCESS'.
